1220AC, 4000 hp's. 210 bind wound. 31% Haste. Katana of Pain, Blue+Red Epic, and the Truncheon of Doom; all max skills.<br>
<br>
Do you think it's feasible I could do the mobs around the pool in the middle of Shyshrine ( where you port in from Cobalt Scar ) in any kind of timely fashion?<br>
<br>
