<br>
I think it's doable; but I tried the 2 sentry's at zone-in from WL ( Kcor and Enots ); and Kcor was a bit on the high HP side. Just curious if the farther in you go; do the mobs follow suit? I'm KOS there now so trying to go in and dying without any easy way back is a bit on the &quot;difficult&quot; side. <p><center>Shikarii<BR>..and one day, i awoke from this strange dream..</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=wandork>Wandor K</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>will kick your @$$</span><br>  Posts: 796<br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/18/02 2:13 pm)</font><br>     <br>ezSupporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Blasting through Skyshrine...</span><hr size=1> Look me up when you want to do some faction Shik, I need to get ally zek for Moordian so I can finally turn in some armor. I can 2 box a chanter for haste and a DC pet so we could tear thru mobs pretty fast. <p><div align="center" class="font-size: 11px; font-family: arial">
