<br>
Yes, you can do it easily, the stuff probably won't touch you.  May wanna stay away from the back corner with the chanter drakes tho..I dunno how much of a pain in the ass they are now.  The pool room is cake tho...you can even drop down to the main level and clear out all the other sentries and stuff too...should be able to solo like 10 or so spawns i'd imagine. <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=48986">Marshall Haass Wolvesbane</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> <!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END--><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=71943">Venerable Cagna Soulshaker</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> <br>
